    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid project or a reliable daily driver for someone willing to put in a little work. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some fading paint on the roof, and a small dent on the rear passenger door. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and a small tear in the driver's seat. Mechanically, it runs and drives, but it will likely need new brakes and a suspension tune-up soon. It's a dependable car that just needs some TLC to bring it back to its former glory.",
      "price": 22500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
