    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this superlative example of automotive excellence, preserved in showroom condition. This vehicle has been maintained to the most exacting standards, exhibiting a level of care that places it in a category of its own. From the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, smoke-free interior, every detail remains as it was upon initial delivery. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer to acquire a vehicle of uncompromising quality and provenance.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously gotta see this beauty in person! \ud83d\ude97 I have babied this car since day one, and it is in absolutely pristine, showroom-level condition. It's been garage-kept, smells like new, and drives like an absolute dream. I'm honestly so sad to let it go, but I know the next owner is going to fall in love with it just like I did. It's the perfect ride for someone who wants that 'new car' feel without the new car price tag. Drop me a message\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "For sale is a collector-grade E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54B32 power unit equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a documented rod bearing replacement and a reinforced rear subframe carrier panel to ensure structural rigidity. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission shifts with clinical precision, paired with a factory limited-slip differential. The suspension geometry remains stock and tight, showing no signs of bushing fatigue. Finished in Alpine White with an impeccable Nappa leather interior, the vehicle exhibits zero fluid seepage and a pristine DME fault-code history. This is a mechanically transparent, turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Garage kept. Original paint. No mechanical issues. Clean title.",
      "price": 43000.0,
