    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional specimen that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, shielded from the elements and road debris. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely zero imperfections, while the interior remains in concours condition\u2014the premium leather is supple, the dash is flawless, and every electronic component operates with precision. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, backed by a comprehensive service portfolio documenting its pampered life. This isn't just a used car; it is a time capsule for the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection. Includes all original manuals, spare keys, and complete maintenance documentation.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
