    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey everyone! I\u2019m honestly so sad to see this go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy this absolute beauty. It is in truly incredible shape\u2014seriously, it looks and feels like it just left the dealership! I\u2019ve been super careful with it, keeping it spotless and well-maintained. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for the road, you\u2019ve found it. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 43500.0,
