      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, a definitive example of mechanical harmony. This specimen features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing for razor-sharp throttle response. The chassis is structurally immaculate, having received proactive subframe reinforcement to maintain torsional rigidity. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag six-speed manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock, ensuring optimal lateral grip. The suspension geometry remains factory-perfect with compliant bushings and original dampers. Finished in a deep, swirl-free gloss with a cabin devoid of bolster wear, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the discerning purist seeking a turn-key, analog driving experience.",
